extends Div
implements com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasName, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasEnabled, HasActive, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasText, HasIcon, HasIconPosition, com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.HasClickHandlers, HasFormValue, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasValue<Boolean>
    A checkbox with a label for use within a Form.

    Basically this is a non-styled CheckBoxButton encapsulated in a Div.

    Sven Jacobs
